high_descs: Move to the stove on the other side of the kitchen.
Pick up a pot on the back burner.
Turn around and move to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the pot on the second self before waiting a moment and picking up the pot again and closing the door.
Move to the cabinet to the right and open it.
Place the pot inside the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Move one of the pots on the stove to the cabinet next to the refrigerator.

high_descs: Pick up the copper pot on the left of the stove.
Bring the pot to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Put pot in cabinet under the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot in a cabinet under the microwave.

high_descs: Go towards the shelf and turn to the right. Walk towards the counter then turn left. Walk straight ahead to the toaster and turn right. Walk straight to the stove.
Pick up the leftmost pot on the stove.
Turn around with the pot. Walk straight towards the fridge and turn left. Turn back towards the fridge again.
Open the fridge and put the pot on the middle shelf and shut the door. Open the door and take the pot back out again.
Turn around so you are facing the stove.
Walk halfway up and turn around facing the cabinet next to the fridge and lower the pot. Open the door and put the pot inside and close it again.
anns.task_desc: To place a pot in the fridge then put it away.
